Subject: (off topic) Amiga and ASDL

Hello,

Sorry for this off topic message, but you guys might have an answer for me.

In the area I live in, the phone company has an ASDL service for very little
money.  I'd like to set up a server using one of my Amigas so I can host
some online gaming.  Do you know if there is router that will allow me to
use an asdl line?

Kind regards
-- 
