> Is it possible to remap to these?  Or will these remap for themselves  (=
ha
> ha, dream on Curt...)
> 
> If it is possible, how?  Will the normal ObtainBestPenA routine work?

ObtainBestPenA will work up to 32bits per colour, as you specify each colo=
ur as 
a long, left justified so that $FF will be the same as $FFFF (you'd use 
$FF000000 and $FFFF0000). So using OBPA_ should give OK results on all sys=
tems 
(unless you are trying to remap a 24bit image onto a 4 colour WB :)

