Curt Esser churned out *this* drivel:
 
> The only way I can get the depth of the WB is by using the Blitz WBdepth
> command or by grabbing the Screen's bitmap, and reading the Blitz bitmap
> object.
> Neither method will work on a GFX card screen, I don't think.
> 
