@NODE "Mail_135" "Re: SV: animation"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Tue, 6 Apr 1999 16:29:09 +0000
From: "Paul" <paulwest@stationone.demon.co.uk>
Organization: private
Date: 6 Apr 99 17:29:15 +0000
Subject: Re: SV: animation
