>> data continuously at the same time as decompression and playback? How
>> about targetting an 6 or 8-speed cd-rom? ;-)


> Errrmm why do you guys want to target those old dinosaurs ? I have a 32x
> cd-rom in my amiga 4000 and a 36x in my work pc. I would have gotten a
> 36x for my amiga as well, but since i bought the amiga cd-rom before the
