Yeah, it's really only gonna work for people with hefty processors, fast
cd-rom drives, monitors and soundcards.  That's aiming a bit /too/ high I
think...

> Then you`d need a compression ratio of 10:1 (pretty tricky and
> probably very lossy) to make any use of that with maybe an eight speed cd
