What it means is it's draws the first horizontal line, skips the second,
draws the third, skips the fourth etc.  It means that when the anim is
made, it can skip out all the black lines (which can be added in via
software as it's playing), half the size of the file while still allowing
you to see what's going on.

>> Anyway, what about that format that was developed for Golem? 6x Cd-ROM
