You need the arctangent of the opposite/adjacent. or 

angle=3Datan((y2-y1)/(x2-x1))

but obviously putting in the corect checks and remembering that this will =
give 
you answers between 0 and pi. You'll need to do checking for angles >180 a=
nd 
<360 (something like angle=3Dangle*Sgn(y2-y1))


