Hello everyone!

I'm trying (trying being the main word here) to make a GUI for
Netconnect 2 for my dad, who hasn't got a clue about computers but
wants to use the internet.

I'm using the Red When Exicted AREXX library (part of the blitz
support suite).

My problem is this: When I send a AREXX message to Final Writer
(useing the "RXSendCommand" command), it seems to ignore me, so
instead I wrote AREXX script and executed in Blitz using the RXExecute
script command, it still ignored me, but if I run the script from
shell, it works! how come? I need to control Final Writer in Blitz.

Can anyone help?

/Richard Brooklyn/

