Well, you DO have it on the CD - it's not what you think, though.  It's on
one of the BSS "disks" in the Basiclibs/ drawer, as BBASLLIB.OBJ

It's one of the updated libraries that the BSS puts into your acidlibs file
during the install.

I've never seen a blitz.library1, although I did find the same page and
tried to find it myself a while back. 

