Subject: BLITZLIST ADMIN VOTE
Date: Sun, 25 Apr 1999 17:16:19 +0200

    Hiya!

I've seen the voting thats been going on, on the list
and I find at all very messy. If you guys want then I
can throw together a voting system, that uses a database
to keep track of the voting. People could add them
selfs as candidates, so people could vote for them.

We could have the page open for 1-2 weeks so that
everyone gets a chance to vote. I can offer online
statistics so you can check the score at anytime.

 Bye!



