Organization: !
Date: 6 Apr 99 18:47:19 +0100
Subject: Re: Code
Encoding: 7bit

On 6 Apr 99 19:10:08 +0000, FreeJack wrote:

> If anybody has ideas to add some code ... tell me

Well, can you detect if the XEN font is present, and use that instead
of Topaz?  Or supply some other cool font that has all the symbols?

Also, each symbol could be inside one little button, which would be
more "intuition" - I guess this is why you ask the next question:

> BTW ... *HOW* can I use GT Gagdgets in such a "handmade" Window ???

It's not too difficult.  Run the Intuitools2 program that's in
examples/tools/ - see what it produces.

