@NODE "Mail_369" "Re: Code"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Wed, 7 Apr 1999 17:21:48 +0100
From: "FreeJack" <Free_Jack@gmx.net>
Date: 7 Apr 99 18:12:25 +0000
Subject: Re: Code
Encoding: 7bit

Hi Evan,

> On 6 Apr 99 19:10:08 +0000, FreeJack wrote:
> 
> > If anybody has ideas to add some code ... tell me
> 
> Well, can you detect if the XEN font is present, and use that instead
> of Topaz?  Or supply some other cool font that has all the symbols?
Hhhmm I have decided to use EXPLIZIT Topaz 8 because

1. Everybody has it (no fall-back routine)

2. Size is known (no autoadjust of window size)

