Hi Tony,

> Can anyone explain how I can get the full name (including path) of the
> current executable program?    I want to extract tooltypes from it's
> Icon.   

Here's what I used in NewStuff:

*ns_task.Task = FindTask_(0) ; get task name for reading icon tooltypes

If *ns_task <> 0
  progname.s = Peek.s(*ns_task\tc_Node\ln_Name)
Else
  progname.s = "NewStuff"
EndIf

