@NODE "Mail_449" "Gadget Trouble"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Fri, 2 Apr 1999 11:54:34 +0000
From: Jake Frederick <gonzo@acadia.net>
Date: Fri, 02 Apr 1999 06:56:48 +0500
Subject: Gadget Trouble

    Is it that no one could answer my question about gadgets or did you just
not see it because my clock was messed up? In case it was the latter, here it
is again:

    Does someone have an example of a functional slider using GTTags? I can
set
the level using GTSetAttrs and  #GTSL_level but for some reason I can't set
the max level length using #GTSL_MaxLevelLen. Also how can I read the active
option on a cycle gadget? 

-- 
-If the doors of perception were cleansed everything would appear to man as it
truly is, infinite.-


