On Fri, 19 Apr 1991 02:21:27 -0500 Curt Esser said:
> Hi Tony
> 
> On 18-Apr-99, Tony Rolfe wrote:
> > 
> > Is it possible to change the text in a GTButton "on the fly"?
> > 
> > If so, how?
> 
