--------

        /\/\/\/\/\                    Fr=E9d=E9ric Laboureur (Fred)
     __/          \_    =

    /^ ^  u^ ^n  ^ ^\               E-Mail Address: alphasnd@sdv.fr =

   (o o_ /(o o)\ _o o)  =

  _/_ /// |   | \\\ _\_              Only Amiga makes it possible
 (o_o)//  (o o)  \\(o_o)            Quality software for the Amiga
