 F-Base  TheBoss  F-Bench         AlphaSOUND - FANTAISIE Software (1999)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------=
--------

--BOUNDARY.1076267008.1
Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="Demo.bb2"


a = %10001  ; 17
b = %00100  ; 4

NPrint a, " ", b

NPrint a|b *2     ; it does (17|4)*2   = 42
NPrint a OR b*2   ; it does 17 | (b*2) = 25

NMouseWait
End


--BOUNDARY.1076267008.1

