@NODE "Mail_516" "Re: Help Please, remap and gtshape"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Tue, 20 Apr 1999 11:57:58 +0100
From: "David McMinn" <D.Mcminn@eee.rgu.ac.uk>
Organization: The Robert Gordon University, E&EE
Date: Tue, 20 Apr 1999 11:55:56 +0100
encoding: Quoted-printable
Subject: Re: Help Please, remap and gtshape

> I need very fast speed remap.
> GTShape function uncorrect with colors.

 Normally GTShapes only work with 4 colours, but that is a bug in the Blit=
z 
library. You can fix it with this code (before doing AttachGTList):

*g.Gadget=3DGTGadPtr(gtlistnr,idnr)
*g\PlanePick=3D0
*img.Image=3D*g\GadgetRender
For i.w=3D0 to *img\Depth-1
    *g\PlanePick =3D *g\PlanePick | (1 LSL i)
Next


|) /\ \/ ][ |)   |\/| =A9 |\/| ][ |\| |\|
 dmcminn@house-of-mojo.freeserve.co.uk
