@NODE "Mail_517" "Re: Help Please, remap and gtshape"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Wed, 21 Apr 1999 03:35:14 +0100
From: "Tony Rolfe" <edgewater@shoalhaven.net.au>
Organization: Edgewater Motel, Burrill Lake, NSW 2539 Australia
Date: 21 Apr 99 12:33:21 +1000
Subject: Re: Help Please, remap and gtshape
Encoding: 7bit

On Tue, 20 Apr 1999 11:55:56 +0100 David McMinn said:
> 
> *g.Gadget=GTGadPtr(gtlistnr,idnr)
> *g\PlanePick=0
> *img.Image=*g\GadgetRender
> For i.w=0 to *img\Depth-1
>     *g\PlanePick = *g\PlanePick | (1 LSL i)
> Next

OK, does the above code mean that you can get the gadget address and
poke values straight into the gadget flags after the GTString and
before the AttachGTList??     Seems that will solve one of my
problems.    Thanks David.

Cheers

