Hi David

On 09-Apr-99, David McMinn wrote:
>> Hi,
>>  I recently discovered the location of the cash data for a Sensible
>> WOrld Of Soccer 95/96 Career file, and prompty edited it to max :)
> 
> No-one will care, isn't there a 97/98 version ;)
