Hi BaH

On 10-Apr-99, BaH wrote:
> 
>> What do you need to do that can't be done with a norml ointer?
> 
> Colours, size, but mainly for animation. I'm sure it's easier to animate a
> qblit mapped to a shape than it is to animate a mouse pointer directly. I
