Jake,

> So it would be quicker and just as easy to just load a bitmap and grab the
> shapes rather than load the shapes, blit them and then grab them right? A
> shapes file probably takes up less room than a bitmap doesn't it? 

Try it and see. If you have a number of shapes and you have to grab
them off from a bitmap anyway, you may as well grab them to chunky.
You could save the chunky data and load it back in later, or do it at
the start of your program.

