Hi all, 

On the tooltype reading subject, I've just made an interesting
discovery - although they're not listed in my autodocs, there are
actually two more commands in icon.library : GetIcon_ () and PutIcon_().

GetIcon_ () 's syntax is name, icon, freelist - I wonder if the
AllocFreeList_ () command would help in adding new tooltypes?

Anyone want to mess about with it ? (since I don't get it at all ;)

See ya,
