I don't want to mess with it, as it looks rather complicated and the
RIlibrary works fine for me  ;)

But, I don't think you want to mess with those commands - I think they are
"internal", as the GetDiskObject_ command automatically sets up the
Freelist and the List for the tooltypes and structure for the images and so
on for you.  And then FreeDiskObject_ takes care of the cleanup afterwards.

