Somewhere Matt Briggs wrote:

MB > Firstly, I am using the command `MUIInsertSingle' to insert lines into the
MB > listview, however when ever the window is resized the listview contents
MB > are lost. Is it possible therefore to overcome this.

Do you have the #MUIM_ListRedraw tag ?

