Organization: Satanic Dreams Software.
Subject: Randomize EEEEK!

Hello,

    Does anyone know why RRND and RND only return a WORD accurate
variable?? And if there is any way to get a random LONG ?
I tried this:

Minm.l=0
Maxm.l=2049567

RRandomize Timer

For a=0 To 100
  Multiples.l=Int(Maxm.l/32768)
  For TMP=0 To Multiples
    TagPos.l+RRnd(0,32768)
  Next
  NPrint TagPos.l
  TagPos.l=0
Next

VWait 200
End
;-------#---#------
;(BTW - this just divides the Maxm by a WORD maximum, and then
; appends the words to a long)

Well I thought it was a clever way to do it ;)
But if you try that you will see that it averages at around 1000000
+/- a couple of hundred-thousand :((.. Never goes anywhere near
0 or 2000000... Which is really dodgy...

Anyone got ANY ideas at all? Pleeeeeeez..

Cya!
