Return a load of Minus numbers?
I guess its the types?
I had to change it to:

Lofs.s="2000000.0"
For a=0 To 100
  NPrint Int(Rnd(1.0)*Val(Lofs))
Next

Which works fine ;).. But it`s a bit of a bodge ;)
Oh well, whatever works ;)

[=> Dave
Regards
-- 
