It sounds similar to a compression system I developed for my self.

My system simply scanned the sample at set frequencies and built a
small table stating the frequency, the starting point and the length.
A special algorithm could use the information to systhesize a new
sound which sounded similar to the original.

it worked well on synthesized sounds, but was poor on real sounds.

compression rates were typically 30K to 1K

