@NODE "Mail_834" "Re: string compression"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Wed, 14 Apr 1999 15:07:44 +0100
From: Chris Deeney <chris@addnet.demon.co.uk>
Date: Wed, 14 Apr 1999 15:02:15 +0000
