Well I have the sample compressor and decompressor. In fact it can use ne=
w
exponential delta too, which in fact gives beter sound quality in 8 bit
sounds. So the idea of the coding is that every byte from the sample is
replaced by one nible, and this nible tells which value from the table of=

-128 -64 -32 -16 -8 -4 -2 -1 0 1 2 4 8 16 32 64  you will add to the
previous sample value (Fibonachi coding uses fibonachi numbers instead of=

power of 2's) This packing method halves the needed space for samples.

-- =


